reviewText: I really don't hate it. I saw it when it was on VHS many years ago and I liked it. This time when I received the DVD it was the wrong region code and I had to return it. I did not know any other way to submit this complaint since you asked for a review.
really a very poorly done movie. tanya roberts is totally waisted un this movie. dialogue is awfull and quite stupid. i am a tanya roberts fan and this was a waste of time.
